    "(108)The ν = -1 state is somewhat different in spirit.",
    "At this filling, we need to fill 3 of the 8 central bands.",
    "We can construct the state as follows.",
    "In one spin species, we preserve all symmetries of the strained BM model and fill 2 of the 4 bands.",
    "As noted previously, this leads to a nematicfoot_44 semimetal."
